  "description": "A remake of the Super Famicom <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Dragon+Quest+VI%3a+Maboroshi+no+Daichi\">role-playing game</a>, <i>Dragon Quest VI: Realms of Revelation</i> is based on the same engine already used for the DS remakes of its two predecessors, <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/dragon-quest-iv-chapters-of-the-chosen\">Chapters of the Chosen</a> and <a id=\"d8f65df743a86ac426b356dc73d0274d3\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Dragon+Quest+V%3a+Hand+of+the+Heavenly+Bride\">Hand of the Heavenly Bride</a>. The game features elaborate 2D sprite animation set in full 3D environments.<br><br>Players set out to counter the threat of a demon overlord by exploring a top-down view world map and dungeons and meet colorful monsters in turn-based, first-person view battles.  Although the game's core gameplay is almost identical to that of others from the main series, instead of a day/night cycle it features two parallel game worlds, a growing team roster from which an adventuring party can be assembled as well as a class system later in the game for further customization.<br><br>In addition, there is a touch screen-based curling mini game as well as a message exchange system utilizing the DS' tag mode feature.",
